\v 11 \add вүҲNow\add* Heber had moved \add withВҰ113542 his wife Yael and their family\add* \add вүҲaway from the other\add* KenitesВҰ113530 (and from Mosheh'sВҰ113536 father-in-law Hobab'sВҰ113534 descendants) and set up his tentВҰ113538 by the oak treeВҰ113541 atВҰ113542 ZaanannimВҰ113542 near KedeshВҰ113547.
