\v 12 \add вүҲWhenВҰ113549\add* SiseraВҰ113550 was told that BarakВҰ113553 (Abinoam'sВҰ113556 son) had gone to MtВҰ113557. TaborВҰ113559,
\v 13 \add *he\add* assembled his warriors and their nineВҰ113569 hundredВҰ113570 chariotsВҰ113568 (with iron on them) \add and went from\add* HaroshetВҰ113580-HaggoyimВҰ113581 to the KishonВҰ113585 riverbed.
