\v 14 вҖңGet going,вҖқ DeborahВҰ113588 told Barak, вҖңbecause it's today thatВҰ113596 YahwehВҰ113598 has gone ahead of you andВҰ113587 \add вүҲwill help you defeat\add* SiseraВҰ113601.вҖқ SoВҰ113587 Barak led his tenВҰ113611 thousandВҰ113612 warriors down from Mt. TaborВҰ113610.
