\v 17 \add вүҲButВҰ113666\add* Sisera had fled onВҰ113668 footВҰ113668 \add and ran to\add* Yael'sВҰ113672 tentВҰ113671 (Heber the Kenite'sВҰ113678 wifeВҰ113673) because there was peaceВҰ113680 between KingВҰ113683 YabinВҰ113682 of Hatsor and the houseВҰ113687 of Heber the Kenite.
\v 18 YaelВҰ113692 went out to meet SiseraВҰ113694 and told him, вҖң\add вүҲStop and rest\add*, my masterВҰ113698. \add вүҲStop and rest here\add*. Don't be afraidВҰ113703.вҖқ SoВҰ113691 he turnedВҰ113704 and went into her tentВҰ113706, and she coveredВҰ113707 him withВҰ113708 a blanket.
