\v 19 вҖңI'm thirstyВҰ113719,вҖқ he said. вҖңCould you get me a littleВҰ113715 waterВҰ113717 to drink.вҖқ \add @Yael\add* openedВҰ113720 a goatskin container andВҰ113710 gave him milk to drink, thenВҰ113710 she coveredВҰ113726 him \add again\add*.
\v 20 вҖңStand at the tentВҰ113732 doorway,вҖқ he saidВҰ113728, вҖңand if anyone comes and asksВҰ113738 you if \add вүҲyou've seen a man\add*, sayВҰ113744, вҖҳNo.вҖҷ вҖқ
