\v 21 ThenВҰ113747 Heber'sВҰ113751 wifeВҰ113749 YaelВҰ113748 got a hammerВҰ113759 and a tentВҰ113755 peg and \add вүҲcrept inВҰ113760 silently\add*, driving the peg through his templeВҰ113768 and pounding it into the ground,. He'd been tired and was sleepingВҰ113773 soundly, and \add вүҲit killed him\add*.
\v 22 \add вүҲMeanwhile\add* BarakВҰ113778 \add вүҲhad been searching for\add* Sisera, and YaelВҰ113784 went out to meet him. вҖңCome inВҰ113804 here,вҖқ she told him, вҖңand I'llВҰ113789 show you the manВҰ113792 you've been searching for.вҖқ He \add вүҲfollowed her into the tent\add* and wowвҖ”Sisera was lyingВҰ113801 there dead withВҰ113804 the peg \add still\add* through his templeВҰ113804.
