\v 13 вҖңNo, however, we'll certainlyВҰ120023 tie you up,вҖқ they \add вүҲreplied\add*, вҖңand we'll handВҰ120022 you over to them. ButВҰ120011 truly we won'tВҰ120024 kill you.вҖқ ThenВҰ120011 they tied him up withВҰ120022 two new ropesВҰ120028 and broughtВҰ120030 him up from the \add #rocks\add*.
