\v 15 He saw a freshВҰ120070 donkey'sВҰ120069 jawboneВҰ120067 \add lying onВҰ120076 the ground\add*, and he reachedВҰ120071 out his handВҰ120072 and \add вүҲgrabbed\add* it, and he slaughtered a thousandВҰ120077 \add Philistine\add* men withВҰ120076 it.
