\v 3 SamsonВҰ120206 \add вүҲstayed withВҰ120213 her\add* untilВҰ120207 the middle of the night, then he got up. He picked up bothВҰ120220 the gates includingВҰ120205 the cross-bar and their postsВҰ120221, and hoisted them up onto his shouldersВҰ120229, and he carriedВҰ120230 them up to the top of the hillВҰ120234 whichВҰ120235 is inВҰ120213 frontВҰ120238 of HebronВҰ120239.
\s1 Shimshon and Delilah
