\v 4 \add вүҲSometime\add* afterВҰ120243 that, \add @Shimshon\add* fell in loveВҰ120246 withВҰ120248 a \add Philistine\add* womanВҰ120247 named DelilahВҰ120251 who \add lived in\add* the SorekВҰ120249 valleyВҰ120248.
\v 5 The Philistine leaders cameВҰ120253 to her and \add вүҲrequested\add*, вҖңMake him open up. \add вүҲFind out what makes him strong, and how we can beat\add* him, so that we can tie him up \add вүҲto keep him inВҰ120262 our power\add*. ThenВҰ120253 we'll each giveВҰ120271 you one thousandВҰ120275 one hundredВҰ120276 silverВҰ120277 coins.вҖқ
