\v 6 SoВҰ120279 DelilahВҰ120280 \add вүҲasked\add* ShimshonВҰ120283, вҖңPlease, tell me \add вүҲwhat makes you so strong\add*, andВҰ120279 how \add вүҲcould someone tie you up to keep you inВҰ120288 their power\add*?вҖқ
