\v 7 вҖңIf they'd tie me up withВҰ120301 sevenВҰ120301 green cordsВҰ120302 thatВҰ120304 haven't been driedВҰ120307,вҖқ \add *he\add* \add вүҲreplied\add*, вҖңthenВҰ120295 I'd becomeВҰ120310 weak andВҰ120295 be just like any other \add #man\add*.вҖқ
