\v 9 Now she had an ambushВҰ120330 \add group\add* \add вүҲready\add* inВҰ120333 the \add next\add* roomВҰ120333 when she saidВҰ120334 to him, вҖңThe PhilistinesВҰ120336 are \add вүҲhere to get\add* you, ShimshonВҰ120338!вҖқ ButВҰ120330 he tore the cordsВҰ120342 to shreds just like a strip of flax fiberВҰ120347 is torn to shreds when \add вүҲthe fireВҰ120349 reaches it\add*, \add вүҲthus\add* \add вүҲthey didn'tВҰ120350 find out\add* \add the secret of\add* his strengthВҰ120352.
\v 10 ThenВҰ120354 DelilahВҰ120355 saidВҰ120354 to \add *him\add*, вҖңListen, you deceivedВҰ120360 me andВҰ120354 lied to me. Now tell me, pleaseВҰ120368, \add вүҲhow could someone tie you up?\add*вҖқ
\p
\v 11 вҖңActually, if theyВҰ120378 would tie me withВҰ120379 new ropesВҰ120379 \add вүҲwhichВҰ120381 have never been used\add*,вҖқ he \add вүҲreplied\add*, вҖңI'd becomeВҰ120387 weak andВҰ120373 be just like any other \add #man\add*.вҖқ
