\v 12 \add вүҲSoВҰ120392\add* DelilahВҰ120393 tookВҰ120392 new cords andВҰ120392 tied him up with them. She saidВҰ120398 to him, вҖңThe PhilistinesВҰ120400 are \add вүҲhere to get\add* you, ShimshonВҰ120402!вҖқ with the ambushВҰ120403 group staying inВҰ120405 the \add next\add* roomВҰ120405. ButВҰ120392 he flicked them off his arms like they were \add just\add* threadВҰ120409.
