\v 13 ThenВҰ120411 DelilahВҰ120412 said to ShimshonВҰ120415, вҖң\add вүҲSo far\add* you'veВҰ120419 \add just\add* \add вүҲbeen deceitfulВҰ120419 to\add* me andВҰ120411 told me lies. \add Now\add* Tell me how you can be tied up.вҖқ
\p So he told her, вҖң\add It's\add* if you just weaveВҰ120432 sevenВҰ120435 locks of my hair into the loom.вҖқ
\p
