\p
\v 23 \add Some time later,\add* the Philistine leaders gatheredВҰ120634 together for a celebration and to offerВҰ120636 a large sacrificeВҰ120637 to theirВҰ120641 god DagonВҰ120640, saying, вҖңOur god has \add вүҲhelped us capture\add* our terrible enemyВҰ120649, ShimshonВҰ120648.вҖқ
\v 24 WhenВҰ120651 the peopleВҰ120653 saw him, they praisedВҰ120654 theirВҰ120657 god, saying, вҖңOurВҰ120673 god has \add вүҲhelped us capture\add* our enemyВҰ120665вҖ”the devastator of our regionВҰ120668 who \add вүҲkilled so many of us\add*.вҖқ
\v 25 \add вүҲLater in the celebration when the drink had liberated theirВҰ120692 thinking\add*, they saidВҰ120680, вҖңCall for Shimshon so he can \add вүҲentertainВҰ120683 us\add*.вҖқ SoВҰ120675 they \add вүҲbrought\add* Shimshon in from the \add вүҲprisonВҰ120689\add* andВҰ120675 \add taunted him\add* \add вүҲto get them all laughing\add*. They made him standВҰ120693 among the pillarsВҰ120696 \add of the building\add*
\v 26 andВҰ120698 \add *he\add* \add вүҲasked\add* the servantВҰ120702 who was \add вүҲguiding him\add* by the handВҰ120704, вҖңPlace my hands againstВҰ120717 the two pillarsВҰ120711 holding up the building \add вүҲso\add* I can lean on them.вҖқ
\v 27 The building was full of the men and the women, \add вүҲincludingВҰ120722\add* the Philistine leaders. On the roof thereВҰ120723 were aboutВҰ120730 threeВҰ120730 thousandВҰ120731 men and women watchingВҰ120734 the entertainment withВҰ120735 ShimshonВҰ120736.
\p
\v 28 ThenВҰ120738 ShimshonВҰ120739 calledВҰ120738 out to Yahweh, вҖңMy masterВҰ120744 Yahweh, please rememberВҰ120746 me. Strengthen me please, just this timeВҰ120751, oh GodВҰ120753, so that I can avengeВҰ120754 myselfВҰ120754 by one \add last\add* act of vengeanceВҰ120755 on the PhilistinesВҰ120760 \add to make them pay for\add* my twoВҰ120758 eyesВҰ120759.вҖқ
\v 29 ThenВҰ120762 \add *he\add* took hold of the twoВҰ120766 centre pillarsВҰ120768 onВҰ120777 whichВҰ120770 the building depended, and \add вүҲpressed out\add* againstВҰ120775 themвҖ”one in his rightВҰ120777 handВҰ120777 and one in his left.
\v 30 ThenВҰ120781 \add *he\add* \add вүҲexclaimed\add*, вҖң\add вүҲLet me\add* die with the PhilistinesВҰ120787!вҖқ He stretchedВҰ120788 out with his strengthВҰ120789 and the building fell onВҰ120789 \add &their\add* leaders and all of the people inВҰ120789 it. \add вүҲSoВҰ120781\add* he killed more people atВҰ120789 his deathВҰ120807 than he had killed during his life.
\p
\v 31 ThenВҰ120813 his brothersВҰ120814 and all his father's householdВҰ120817 wentВҰ120813 \add to Gaza\add* and carriedВҰ120819 \add @his body\add* back. They buriedВҰ120823 himВҰ120824 between ZorahВҰ120826 and EshtaolВҰ120828 inВҰ120829 the burial place of his father ManoahВҰ120830. He had \add вүҲhelped\add* YisraelВҰ120836 for twentyВҰ120837 years.
\c 17
\s1 The false gods of Mikiyas
