\p
\v 1 \add вүҲNow\add* there was a manВҰ120843 named MicahВҰ120848 from the hill country of EphraimВҰ120846
\v 2 who \add вүҲadmitted\add* to his mother, вҖңThose \add вүҲeleven\add* hundredВҰ120853 silver coins thatВҰ120855 were takenВҰ120856 from youвҖ”\add вүҲwhen you made\add* a curseВҰ120861, andВҰ120850 \add вүҲeven said it when I was listening\add*, \add well\add* listen, \add вүҲI've got it all\add*вҖ”I took it myself.вҖқ
\p His mother said, вҖңMay YahwehВҰ120875 blessВҰ120873 you, my son.вҖқ
