\v 6 \add вүҲSoВҰ121864\add* the two of them ateВҰ121865 and drankВҰ121868 togetherВҰ121867, and thenВҰ121864 the woman'sВҰ121871 fatherВҰ121870 saidВҰ121869, вҖңPlease stay \add another\add* nightВҰ121878. \add вүҲRelax and have a goodВҰ121879 time\add*.вҖқ
