\v 7 The manВҰ121883 got ready to leave, however his father-in-law persisted, so he stayed \add another\add* nightВҰ121890 thereВҰ121891.
\v 8 He got up earlyВҰ121893 in the morningВҰ121894 onВҰ121894 the fifthВҰ121896 day to get ready to leave, butВҰ121893 the fatherВҰ121900 of the youngВҰ121901 womanВҰ121901 said, вҖң\add вүҲGet some energy first\add*.вҖқ SoВҰ121893 they waited untilВҰ121907 later in the day, andВҰ121893 thenВҰ121893 the two of them ate.
